{"tid":1597253,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"下次騎劫「對話平台」做「宣傳大台」咪得囉！","createTime":"2019-09-27T01:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T12:21:09.000Z","uid":263448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"38ebe6981bf347b8cbd6a7583f69e2add72af466","tid":1597253,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:08:21.000Z","msg":"上去做騷又話中計，唔去做騷又話中計。<br />\n<br />\n咁下次又黎「對話平台」，抽中既人入tg谷，或者係社交平台宣傳。<br />\n<br />\n收集好意見，或者臨場用手機收集意見，去講。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一致口剔</span>，係公開場合下，<span style=\"color: red;\">要求政府承諾</span>，係遊行其間，警隊不派卧底，不干預遊行，不命令港鐵封站。<br />\n<br />\n係電視前叫777收番警方啲武器，叫佢一係公投，一係批准市民遊行表達意見。<br />\n<br />\n再順勢<span style=\"color: red;\">叫777唔好再係區選搞陰謀手段</span>，咁做只會激化示威活動。<br />\n<br />\n最後，就話對話平台只會左耳入右耳出，<span style=\"color: red;\">未見政府有回應五大訴求，連最基本既獨立調查都無承諾</span>，呼籲各位市民下次唔好再中計，<span style=\"color: red;\">由佢地抽籤抽啲藍絲，圍爐取暖。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只要第2次平台抽極都一致口剔，咁市民表達夠意見，第3次抽埋啲藍絲，政府根本兜唔到話「大多數」，只能夠叫演員扮黃。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e86f0e9c429168244d13f06ebef42b16c0505cc0","tid":1597253,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c108180b666d8b0cde108bc63b8d48352915882f","tid":1597253,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586790151175d329956015750542d56ff77b6263","tid":1597253,"uid":231514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:31:19.000Z","msg":"呼籲啲人對住個cam講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9324f29141dd5ffb8ef7ca901b120cf6ec4d9f7e","tid":1597253,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class